1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:02,740
=Episode 4=

2
00:00:09,260 --> 00:00:10,220
Dr. Gu.

3
00:00:11,500 --> 00:00:13,100
(Doctor's Office 2)

4
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:14,140
Dr. Gu.

5
00:00:14,140 --> 00:00:15,660
- I'm going back to the office.
- Okay.

6
00:00:24,980 --> 00:00:26,140
Dr. Gu.

7
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:31,420
Here you are.

8
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:35,900
Dr. Gu.

9
00:00:39,340 --> 00:00:40,940
Are you doing radio gymnastics

10
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:42,100
in front of my office?

11
00:00:43,100 --> 00:00:44,020
Dr. Gu.

12
00:00:47,980 --> 00:00:48,620
What's the matter?

13
00:00:48,620 --> 00:00:50,140
Look! The aliens.

14
00:00:51,460 --> 00:00:52,500
Lin Zhixiao!

15
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:54,700
Not me. It's your illusion.

16
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:09,780
The subscriber you dialed is busy.

17
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:11,660
Please try later.

18
00:01:20,140 --> 00:01:22,140
(EMK: Have you ticked off
these scenic spots?)

19
00:01:22,140 --> 00:01:24,340
(Sansan: Coffee is delicious)

20
00:01:53,900 --> 00:01:54,740
Sansan.

21
00:01:55,060 --> 00:01:55,780
What's the matter?

22
00:01:55,980 --> 00:01:56,900
I was wrong.

23
00:01:57,300 --> 00:01:58,620
That day,

24
00:01:58,620 --> 00:02:00,020
I didn't know clearly…

25
00:02:00,620 --> 00:02:01,820
If you

26
00:02:01,820 --> 00:02:03,140
are still not creative like this,

27
00:02:03,300 --> 00:02:04,740
I advise you to stop.

28
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:15,900
(I've done a lot of wrongs.)

29
00:02:15,900 --> 00:02:18,620
(I can't read your mind.)

30
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:20,460
(I don't know what you think
of our relationship.)

31
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:30,060
(I will always like you until…)

32
00:02:30,060 --> 00:02:32,220
(old me old you)

33
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:36,180
Are you paying tribute

34
00:02:36,260 --> 00:02:37,740
to Love Actually?

35
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:39,940
It doesn't matter what I pay tribute to.

36
00:02:44,540 --> 00:02:45,260
Don't you answer it?

37
00:02:45,260 --> 00:02:45,980
She is not important.

38
00:02:45,980 --> 00:02:46,980
My priority

39
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:48,220
is you now.

40
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:52,580
If I create inconveniences,

41
00:02:52,580 --> 00:02:53,260
I can give you a minute.

42
00:02:53,260 --> 00:02:54,420
No, no, no.

43
00:02:54,420 --> 00:02:55,060
You didn't.

44
00:02:55,140 --> 00:02:56,140
It's very convenient.

45
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:57,300
Nothing inconvenient.

46
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:58,500
It's just a video call.

47
00:02:58,780 --> 00:03:00,220
You can just watch it right here.

48
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:04,500
Hello.

49
00:03:04,980 --> 00:03:06,220
Gu Xiao.

50
00:03:06,660 --> 00:03:08,100
When are you coming to see me?

51
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:10,740
I...

52
00:03:10,980 --> 00:03:12,620
What are you doing, Gu Xiao?

53
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:13,980
Gu Xiao.

54
00:03:13,980 --> 00:03:15,180
- Gu Xiao.
- Bye.

55
00:03:15,540 --> 00:03:17,220
Why didn't you call me?

56
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:19,940
Call me.

57
00:03:20,820 --> 00:03:23,260
Gu Xiao, what are you doing?

58
00:03:23,580 --> 00:03:25,380
I have some proper business to do now.

59
00:03:25,380 --> 00:03:27,140
I will call you later.

60
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:27,860
Bye.

61
00:03:39,740 --> 00:03:40,660
Lin Zhixiao.

62
00:03:41,460 --> 00:03:43,820
Dr. Gu, I've been waiting for you.

63
00:03:44,900 --> 00:03:45,940
What are you doing here?

64
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:47,100
I'm here...

65
00:03:49,980 --> 00:03:50,900
I... I...

66
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:52,780
I was just waiting for you
in your office.

67
00:03:52,780 --> 00:03:54,100
I noticed you weren't there,

68
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:55,700
so I have to wait for you here.

69
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:01,860
I'm dining out.

70
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:03,260
You can come with me.

71
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:05,940
(Doctor's Lounge)

72
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:06,940
Okay!

73
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:10,620
Dr. Gu, let me treat you.

74
00:04:20,540 --> 00:04:22,740
Sansan, emergency!

75
00:04:22,740 --> 00:04:24,300
I need to find a restaurant
nearby the hospital

76
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:26,540
to treat Dr. Gu.

77
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:28,980
A high-end one.
Quickly recommend me one.

78
00:04:34,740 --> 00:04:36,060
- Hello.
- Hello.

79
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:36,700
(If time could stop at the moment)
Only the two of you?

80
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:37,700
(when we first met)
Yeah, I made an appointment.

81
00:04:37,700 --> 00:04:39,140
- Okay, this way, please.
- Ms. Lin.

82
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:42,340
Is this place good?

83
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:44,900
- Yeah, it's delicious. Trust me.
- This way.

84
00:04:47,220 --> 00:04:47,900
Here.

85
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:48,780
Thank you.

86
00:04:58,500 --> 00:05:00,860
Is this the seat we reserved?

87
00:05:00,860 --> 00:05:01,620
Yes, it is.

88
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:06,060
Thank you.

89
00:05:07,700 --> 00:05:08,900
This is our menu.

90
00:05:09,740 --> 00:05:10,700
Thank you.

91
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:12,420
Today is Couple Theme Day.

92
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:13,900
Couple Theme Day?

93
00:05:15,660 --> 00:05:17,340
I'm sorry, I-I don't know

94
00:05:17,340 --> 00:05:18,660
today is a special...

95
00:05:19,540 --> 00:05:20,860
We have three packages.

96
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:22,100
For 288 yuan,

97
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:22,940
388 yuan

98
00:05:22,940 --> 00:05:24,020
and 588 yuan respectively.

99
00:05:24,220 --> 00:05:25,660
Which one would you like?

100
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:27,420
Talk to me. Talk to me. It's my treat.

101
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:30,020
Got it.

102
00:05:30,020 --> 00:05:31,660
Looks like your girlfriend's
in charge of the money.

103
00:05:33,340 --> 00:05:34,180
No, no, no.

104
00:05:34,180 --> 00:05:35,060
No, no, no.

105
00:05:35,300 --> 00:05:36,020
Just...

106
00:05:36,020 --> 00:05:38,300
What kind of package do you want?

107
00:05:39,940 --> 00:05:41,500
In our 588 yuan package,

108
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:42,580
there is an upgraded dessert,

109
00:05:42,580 --> 00:05:43,780
heart-shaped tiramisu.

110
00:05:43,780 --> 00:05:45,340
Its name is Devotion.

111
00:05:45,340 --> 00:05:46,620
It has a good meaning.

112
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:47,940
Would you like to try it?

113
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:49,740
No, it's okay. It's okay.

114
00:05:49,740 --> 00:05:51,020
I'll choose myself.

115
00:05:57,020 --> 00:05:58,660
We'll have a 288 yuan package.

116
00:05:58,940 --> 00:05:59,500
Thank you.

117
00:05:59,500 --> 00:06:00,740
Okay, just a minute.

118
00:06:10,380 --> 00:06:11,340
Lin Zhixiao,

119
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:12,660
I thought you were looking for me

120
00:06:12,660 --> 00:06:14,260
because you want to ask about
your father's surgical plan.

121
00:06:14,620 --> 00:06:15,740
Looks like now

122
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:17,860
there's something even harder to say.

123
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:19,700
Lin Zhixiao.

124
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:22,020
Well…

125
00:06:26,740 --> 00:06:27,940
You can't really be

126
00:06:27,940 --> 00:06:29,260
looking for a date.

127
00:06:29,260 --> 00:06:30,260
No, no, Dr. Gu.

128
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:31,380
Don't get me wrong.

129
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:32,700
I didn't mean that.

130
00:06:33,060 --> 00:06:34,100
I just...

131
00:06:34,940 --> 00:06:36,420
It's...

132
00:06:37,020 --> 00:06:38,340
not easy to ask.

133
00:06:38,340 --> 00:06:39,220
But

134
00:06:39,940 --> 00:06:41,260
I still have to ask.

135
00:06:41,820 --> 00:06:42,660
It's...

136
00:06:48,500 --> 00:06:49,300
Dr. Gu,

137
00:06:49,300 --> 00:06:50,900
please operate on my father.

138
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:52,260
Thank you.

139
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:17,620
Wei, you're not home yet.

140
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:19,860
Du, you're just in time.

141
00:07:19,860 --> 00:07:20,620
Come here.

142
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:21,220
Okay.

143
00:07:21,260 --> 00:07:22,820
Handle this as usual.

144
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:25,380
After the patient's family do this,

145
00:07:25,380 --> 00:07:26,900
they will feel at ease.

146
00:07:27,140 --> 00:07:28,420
Who sent it this time?

147
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:29,620
Lin Zhixiao.

148
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:31,660
Lin Zhixiao?

149
00:07:31,660 --> 00:07:32,380
Yeah.

150
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:33,700
She gave you a red envelope.

151
00:07:33,700 --> 00:07:35,180
Does that mean you're not leaving

152
00:07:35,180 --> 00:07:36,860
and you're going to operate
on Lin Jianguo?

153
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:40,740
She's not asking me to do my best
in surgery.

154
00:07:40,740 --> 00:07:42,300
But she misunderstood me

155
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:43,660
because I don't want to
operate on her father.

156
00:07:45,460 --> 00:07:46,180
It's okay.

157
00:07:46,460 --> 00:07:47,700
Anyway, in two days,

158
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:49,300
my transfer application
will be approved.

159
00:08:09,580 --> 00:08:10,500
That one.

160
00:08:16,500 --> 00:08:17,380
Does it hurt?

161
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:19,260
It's okay.

162
00:08:24,980 --> 00:08:25,980
I have paid the bills.

163
00:08:26,260 --> 00:08:26,940
Mm.

164
00:08:28,020 --> 00:08:28,980
Zhixiao.

165
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:30,340
Why don't you go get me something?

166
00:08:30,340 --> 00:08:31,980
Come out and I'll tell you
how to get there.

167
00:08:31,980 --> 00:08:33,740
It's alright.

168
00:08:39,660 --> 00:08:41,380
What's the matter, Ms. Li?

169
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:44,580
The red envelope is returned.

170
00:08:44,740 --> 00:08:45,740
Red envelope?

171
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:47,420
Red envelope for Dr. Gu?

172
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:49,180
I went to pick up your dad's medicine.

173
00:08:49,180 --> 00:08:50,420
When I was paying,

174
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:52,500
I found out that there is more money
in the card.

175
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:54,300
It is just the amount of the red envelope.

176
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:55,740
If it wasn't him, who could it be?

177
00:08:56,180 --> 00:08:58,740
Dr. Gu returned the red envelope.

178
00:09:00,380 --> 00:09:02,380
Do you think he thinks we paid less?

179
00:09:02,380 --> 00:09:04,140
Or are there other reasons?

180
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:05,220
Who knows?

181
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:07,380
I think he's made up his mind

182
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:08,940
not to operate on your dad.

183
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:12,060
Come on, Ms. Li.

184
00:09:12,060 --> 00:09:13,260
Don't worry about it.

185
00:09:13,260 --> 00:09:14,100
I'll convince him.

186
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:15,700
What can you do?

187
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:17,500
No worries.

188
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:19,100
I'll take care of it, okay?

189
00:09:20,660 --> 00:09:22,060
All right, get inside.

190
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:36,420
Dr. Gu, what a coincidence!

191
00:09:36,420 --> 00:09:37,940
I was looking for you.

192
00:09:38,300 --> 00:09:39,900
Dr. Gu, I think you're a very good

193
00:09:39,900 --> 00:09:41,460
and responsible doctor.

194
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:42,700
I don't know

195
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:43,780
what happened to me before,

196
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:45,140
but I took leave of my sense,

197
00:09:45,140 --> 00:09:46,740
and I said something strange

198
00:09:46,740 --> 00:09:47,980
and stupid to you.

199
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:49,100
I was wrong. I'm sorry.

200
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:50,300
I won't say that again.

201
00:09:50,300 --> 00:09:51,420
Our Dr. Gu is a…

202
00:09:53,380 --> 00:09:54,860
It's dangerous to walk
like this in the hospital.

203
00:09:54,860 --> 00:09:56,180
Please walk properly.

204
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:57,140
Okay.

205
00:09:57,380 --> 00:09:58,820
Our Dr. Gu cares so much

206
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:00,820
about our patients' family.

207
00:10:00,820 --> 00:10:01,780
Dr. Gu.

208
00:10:01,780 --> 00:10:03,180
I know you must have a reason

209
00:10:03,180 --> 00:10:04,860
why you can't do the surgery,

210
00:10:04,860 --> 00:10:05,980
but do tell.

211
00:10:05,980 --> 00:10:07,740
If you tell me,
we can solve it together.

212
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:09,100
- If you don't, how are we…?
- Hey, Du.

213
00:10:09,100 --> 00:10:10,860
- Dr. Gu, anything I can do for you?
- Oh, right.

214
00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:12,220
Bed 25 needs to have
the medication changed.

215
00:10:12,220 --> 00:10:13,580
Bed 45 needs to have
the drainage tube removed.

216
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:15,420
Bed 46 needs to be discharged.

217
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:16,300
Have you done them all?

218
00:10:16,300 --> 00:10:17,220
Of course, Dr. Gu.

219
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:18,620
You've already told me

220
00:10:18,620 --> 00:10:19,260
when you're on your ward rounds.

221
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:21,020
You told me to take care of them soon.

222
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:22,180
I've already done it

223
00:10:22,180 --> 00:10:23,980
and submitted all the records
to the nurse station.

224
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:25,060
I know

225
00:10:25,060 --> 00:10:26,500
I told you this morning.

226
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,980
I'm just reminding you

227
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:29,540
so you don't make any mistakes.

228
00:10:29,860 --> 00:10:30,700
And,

229
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:32,020
have you written the index of the paper

230
00:10:32,020 --> 00:10:32,860
I asked you to write?

231
00:10:32,860 --> 00:10:34,180
Not only is there
a problem with the index,

232
00:10:34,180 --> 00:10:36,140
but there are also
many omissions in your literature.

233
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:37,260
I've rewritten it all.

234
00:10:37,980 --> 00:10:40,060
What's wrong with you today?
You didn't sleep well?

235
00:10:40,060 --> 00:10:41,900
Last night in the office,

236
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:43,300
you guided me to correct my paper.

237
00:10:44,940 --> 00:10:45,740
Very well.

238
00:10:48,060 --> 00:10:48,940
Did you eat?

239
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:50,780
What did you eat?

240
00:10:51,100 --> 00:10:52,580
Wei, don't scare me.

241
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:54,180
Did I do something wrong?

242
00:10:54,220 --> 00:10:55,500
Just tell me.

243
00:10:55,500 --> 00:10:57,100
What are you talking about?

244
00:10:57,100 --> 00:10:58,780
I'm just caring about

245
00:10:58,780 --> 00:10:59,980
your daily life.

246
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:04,340
Thank you for your care, Dr. Gu.

247
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:06,300
I'm assisting Dr. Chen's surgery.

248
00:11:06,300 --> 00:11:07,420
I need to get ready for it.

249
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:08,620
I really need to go.

250
00:11:12,860 --> 00:11:13,500
Sure, go.

251
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:15,100
Thank you, Dr. Gu.

252
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:16,500
Oh, right, Xiaowei…

253
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:17,420
Dr. Du is not available,

254
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:18,980
but I am, Dr. Gu.

255
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:20,660
Lin Zhixiao.

256
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:22,700
Your father doesn't need you
to take care of him today?

257
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:24,100
- Do you have a lot of time?
- Yes.

258
00:11:24,100 --> 00:11:25,700
Don't waste time on me.

259
00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:27,580
Dr. Gu.

260
00:11:27,580 --> 00:11:29,060
Mr. Lin is in very good condition.

261
00:11:29,060 --> 00:11:30,780
I have plenty of time.

262
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:34,780
- You have nothing to do, right?
- Yes.

263
00:11:35,420 --> 00:11:36,820
I'm suddenly hungry.

264
00:11:36,820 --> 00:11:37,820
Get me something to eat.

265
00:11:38,820 --> 00:11:40,660
The whole wheat bread
I bought this morning.

266
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:41,740
Please enjoy it, Dr. Gu.

267
00:11:43,300 --> 00:11:45,260
I'm thirsty and I don't want to eat.

268
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:46,540
Taken care of that, too.

269
00:11:46,740 --> 00:11:47,980
The cup has been sanitized

270
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:49,420
and has wolfberries in it.

271
00:11:49,420 --> 00:11:50,580
I made it myself.

272
00:11:51,700 --> 00:11:53,300
I'm not thirsty now either.

273
00:11:53,700 --> 00:11:54,660
Where do you want to go?

274
00:11:54,660 --> 00:11:55,660
I'm coming with you, Dr. Gu.

275
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:57,500
Dr. Gu.

276
00:11:57,500 --> 00:11:58,780
Wait for me.

277
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:00,380
Where are you going?

278
00:12:04,180 --> 00:12:04,980
Coming inside?

279
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:06,580
No, no.

280
00:12:06,580 --> 00:12:07,980
Suit yourself, Dr. Gu.

281
00:12:10,700 --> 00:12:12,780
I'll wait for you at the door, Dr. Gu.

282
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:14,900
No rush. Take your time.

283
00:12:28,780 --> 00:12:29,740
Hello, Director.

284
00:12:29,740 --> 00:12:30,580
Mm.

285
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:33,300
