00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:47,460
I don't want Dr. Yan.

328
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:48,580
I want Dr. Gu!

329
00:14:48,580 --> 00:14:49,580
I want Dr. Gu!

330
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:51,340
Dr. Gu is the best!

331
00:14:51,340 --> 00:14:53,140
Dr. Yan is also very good.

332
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:54,300
Yes, Qiuqiu.

333
00:14:54,300 --> 00:14:55,740
Dr. Yan is very good.

334
00:14:56,260 --> 00:14:57,620
