00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:03,940
Don't be angry.

339
00:15:03,940 --> 00:15:04,860
It's okay. It's okay.

340
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:06,780
Come on, Qiuqiu, Ultraman.

341
00:15:06,780 --> 00:15:08,020
Be like him.

342
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:09,540
Qiuqiu.

343
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:10,620
Don't cry. Don't cry.

344
00:15:10,620 --> 00:15:11,380
- Be good, Qiuqiu.
- Here, Ultraman.

