400
00:19:15,980 --> 00:19:17,460
No way.

401
00:19:17,460 --> 00:19:18,980
I can fix it.

402
00:19:18,980 --> 00:19:20,580
Hold on.

403
00:19:36,620 --> 00:19:38,900
Look, well bandaged.

404
00:19:41,300 --> 00:19:42,020
