00:19:56,100 --> 00:19:57,260
Because of my teacher.

406
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:01,100
I couldn't save him.

407
00:20:02,780 --> 00:20:04,020
So now

408
00:20:04,020 --> 00:20:05,260
my shaking hands

409
00:20:05,700 --> 00:20:07,900
are caused by my mental disorder.

410
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:10,020
So

411
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:12,020
I shouldn't have surgery on anyone

412
00:20:12,220 --> 00:20:14,460
in this situation.

