00:22:52,940 --> 00:22:54,980
Yes.

437
00:23:14,700 --> 00:23:15,500
Do you dare?

438
00:23:15,660 --> 00:23:17,020
So exciting.

439
00:23:17,740 --> 00:23:19,020
I like it.

440
00:23:26,180 --> 00:23:27,420
So it's not that

