466
00:26:22,540 --> 00:26:23,260
Hello.

467
00:26:27,420 --> 00:26:28,820
Feel free.

468
00:26:29,300 --> 00:26:31,780
We're not in the office now.

469
00:26:31,780 --> 00:26:32,740
You can hold your hands.

470
00:26:33,140 --> 00:26:34,020
It's okay.

471
00:26:34,900 --> 00:26:36,220
It's so kind of you

472
00:26:36,220 --> 00:26:37,580
to visit him in person.

