475
00:26:40,180 --> 00:26:41,220
So we came to visit him.

476
00:26:41,220 --> 00:26:42,460
That's it, Ms. Li.

477
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:43,900
It's Zhixiao's fault.

478
00:26:43,900 --> 00:26:44,980
Mr. Lin is sick and hospitalized.

479
00:26:44,980 --> 00:26:46,500
She didn't tell us

480
00:26:46,500 --> 00:26:47,540
about such a big thing.

481
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:49,580
Lin Zhixiao did the right thing.

482
00:26:49,980 --> 00:26:51,700
I just got a gastric ulcer.

483
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:53,100
You don't have to be nervous.

484
00:26:53,500 --> 00:26:54,620
I feel

485
00:26:54,620 --> 00:26:55,780
your kindness.

486
00:26:56,100 --> 00:26:56,820
I am so happy.

487
00:26:57,260 --> 00:26:58,300
Exactly.

