496
00:27:15,980 --> 00:27:17,220
If appropriate,

497
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:19,820
you may consider studying abroad
for postgraduate study.

498
00:27:19,820 --> 00:27:20,460
Yes.

499
00:27:21,100 --> 00:27:22,220
By the way, Mr. Lin,

500
00:27:22,260 --> 00:27:23,180
we heard that

501
00:27:23,180 --> 00:27:24,820
the Faculty of Music over there is
also very good.

502
00:27:24,820 --> 00:27:26,980
We can get some information back
for Zhixiao.

503
00:27:28,540 --> 00:27:29,820
Be careful then.

504
00:27:31,140 --> 00:27:33,420
She may lose face abroad.

505
00:27:34,260 --> 00:27:35,500
Mr. Lin.

506
00:27:35,500 --> 00:27:38,180
Keep the bottom line
for further contact.

507
00:27:38,180 --> 00:27:40,260
If I achieve something in the future,

508
00:27:40,260 --> 00:27:41,540
I will take Ms. Li abroad

509
00:27:41,540 --> 00:27:42,780
instead of you.

510
00:27:42,780 --> 00:27:44,740
Don't blame me for being stingy then.

511
00:27:45,620 --> 00:27:46,940
By then,

512
00:27:46,940 --> 00:27:49,300
I will be grey-haired, teetering

513
00:27:49,300 --> 00:27:50,740
