514
00:27:50,820 --> 00:27:52,100
I won't travel anymore.

515
00:27:55,460 --> 00:27:56,300
Zhixiao.

516
00:27:56,860 --> 00:27:58,620
Prepare fruit for them.

517
00:27:58,620 --> 00:28:00,500
- Yes, wash the apples.
- Okay.

518
00:28:00,500 --> 00:28:02,300
- Take a seat. Feel free.
- Take a seat.

519
00:28:02,300 --> 00:28:04,180
You take a seat. I will go with Zhixiao.

520
00:28:04,180 --> 00:28:05,380
- Let's go.
- Okay, let's go.

521
00:28:07,340 --> 00:28:08,060
Let's go.

522
00:28:09,420 --> 00:28:10,260
Zhixiao.

523
00:28:11,900 --> 00:28:14,780
I heard from Sansan

524
00:28:15,180 --> 00:28:17,820
that Mr. Lin…

525
00:28:20,380 --> 00:28:21,100
Yes.

526
00:28:21,340 --> 00:28:22,180
Gastric cancer.

527
00:28:23,540 --> 00:28:25,140
But no one told him.

528
00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:26,060
It was kept secret.

529
00:28:26,100 --> 00:28:27,340
Just keep it in mind.

530
00:28:29,380 --> 00:28:32,380
