541
00:28:50,300 --> 00:28:51,500
It's okay.

542
00:28:53,460 --> 00:28:54,780
Not a big deal.

543
00:28:55,140 --> 00:28:56,820
Why so sad?

544
00:28:58,020 --> 00:28:59,540
Let me tell you something happy.

545
00:28:59,540 --> 00:29:00,220
Okay.

546
00:29:00,500 --> 00:29:01,380
Good news.

547
00:29:01,780 --> 00:29:02,940
