in the summer show.

557
00:29:16,700 --> 00:29:18,220
What good news is this?

558
00:29:18,220 --> 00:29:19,300
What does it have to do with me?

559
00:29:19,580 --> 00:29:21,020
Come on.

560
00:29:21,020 --> 00:29:22,180
Why are you so heartless?

561
00:29:22,180 --> 00:29:23,780
Think about it. If she's absent,

562
00:29:23,780 --> 00:29:25,220
