563
00:29:25,420 --> 00:29:26,860
Who else can play the cello?

564
00:29:27,100 --> 00:29:28,500
Only you!

565
00:29:31,460 --> 00:29:33,060
It makes sense!

566
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:36,980
